quote.summary: Yeahka Ltd is an investment holding company. Through its subsidiaries, the Company is principally engaged in the provision of one-stop payment services, merchant solution services and in-store e-commerce services to retail merchants and consumers. The Company operates three businesses. One-stop payment services business provides merchants for their acceptance of non-cash payments from consumers, through connecting the merchants with the payment networks. Merchant solutions services business includes the provision of various SaaS products with scenario-specific functionalities integrated with the payment services, data analysis services or SaaS terminals with operating system can be customized by customers as needed, agency services to customers, online marketing services to customers, technology services to insurance companies, small-sized loans. The Company also provides in-store e-commerce services. The Company conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
